    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四上手",
        "焦赞",
        "禁子",
        "解子"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、解子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉命差遣，概不由己。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自家，长解的便是。奉了上司公文，将焦赞发配沙漠海岛。天色尚早，伙计们，"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大家往监中走走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、解子同走小圆场，同归上场门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到了监门啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们几位先在那边小茶馆等我，我进监干差使去，咱们回来见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是快着点。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，开监门哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（禁子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "敢是坐监的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你才是坐监的哪！我是上差老爷，我来提差使来啦，快些开门罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我拿钥匙开门，请进来罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解子进监。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "提什么差使？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这里可有个焦赞吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，别提他的名字，看他听见不答应，我们称呼他焦二太爷，还不愿意哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，我说这个差使，都叫你们惯起来了啦，你把他叫出来，就说上差老爷到了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请他出来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫他出来！你怕他，我不怕他，叫他出来罢，你回来听我的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请焦二太爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五凤楼前闯下祸，落得今天受折磨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "禁子，请你二太爷出来，有何话讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上差到了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我见过。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上差在哪里？上差在哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这半天还不出来见我。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二太爷你哪瞧，这就是上差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好个王八日的，这样大模大样的，滚开罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解子倒。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿，哪的西瓜皮，滑了我一个跟斗。倒是他，出来没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你瞧，出来啦，你都不知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我喇呼吗，在哪儿啦？"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你往上看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就是他，煤铺的二掌柜的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你见过他罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你瞧我的，咱给他一个厉害。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瞧你的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上面敢是焦……"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "焦二太爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你也是怕他呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁说不是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解差到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你哪大喜啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜从何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将你发配了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "发配哪里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "沙漠海岛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "几时起程？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "即刻起程。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，开了监门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞、解子、禁子同出监。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "禁子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷子，他可走了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（禁子下。四上手同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "过来，过去。众位见过焦二太爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见焦二太爷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢了。他们都是做什么的？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这都是一路之上伺候你哪的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，这也罢了。解差，将你二太爷这刑法去掉。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，我们不敢作弊，去不得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去与不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不能去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你当真的不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当真的不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然不去？"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不去我就打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你哪别打，瞒上不瞒下，我给你哪去啦就是了。咳，去掉了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你要带上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我不能带上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不带上我就打。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，别打你哪，我也瞒上不瞒下，我也带上罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "解差，这也有个名堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么名堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这叫倒发解。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，不错。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱行哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
