      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘立华上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夫妻双双开店房，开店房，打劫客旅与经商。有人住了咱的店。三更不死见阎"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "数板",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王，见阎王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "运去生姜不辣，时来扁担开花。煮熟了兔儿会跑，打好了豆腐生芽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自家，夜行鬼刘立华的便是。夫妻二人，在这三岔路口，开了一座黑店，买卖"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "倒也茂盛。这几日大雨临门，无有上门的买卖，看今日天气晴和，不免将老婆"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤将出来，将招牌幌儿挂起，有几个倒运的，也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老婆哪里？老婆哪里？呔，老婆哪里！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听大郎唤，急忙到跟前。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大郎请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老婆请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大郎唤我出来，有何吩咐？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看这几日大雨临门，也没有上门的买卖。今日天气晴和，将你唤出，将招牌儿"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挂起，有几个倒运的也未可知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此大郎请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻拿幌子，刘立华翻筋斗，下。刘妻台柱坐。焦赞上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趱行！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、解子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天色已晚，前去打店。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我就是这么样子去打店吗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，瞒上不瞒下，也给你去掉了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，这条道路我不常走，也不知哪是店？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解子碰刘妻。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "瞧人哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎哎哎，我说大嫂子借光你哪，哪是店哪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你没长着眼睛吗，这就是店！"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "巧啦，我们是睡觉的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "投宿的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "睡觉的吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "投宿的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "睡觉的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不会讲话，换一个会讲话的前来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二爷我碰了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店主婆请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可有上房？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有上房，客官请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打进去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官用些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前途用过，孤灯一盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "灯到。请问客官一处安歇，两下安歇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两处安歇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（焦赞下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们在哪儿睡，拿个灯亮儿来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘妻",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随我来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘妻自上场门进。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "解子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伙计们，关门睡呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（解子、四上手同下。刘妻望，下。）"
        }
      ],
