    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "任堂惠",
        "刘立华",
        "焦赞"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。他在前面走，俺在后面跟，赶到此处，为何不见？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“三岔口”，“三岔口”。此处是一客店，想必住在里面。待我店中走走。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘立华上，翻跟斗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷，敢是住店吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠进店，坐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "店家，店家，店家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在这哪，客官用些什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前途用过，孤灯一盏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "放下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唤你再来，不唤你去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为何去而复转？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "客官呼唤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘立华下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。看店家眉来眼去，定是黑店。待我搜店便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠搜，上桌躺。刘立华上，剥门，摸黑摸刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘立华",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，看刀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠、刘立华同打起，任堂惠上房打龙，刘立华倒。焦赞上，开门，任堂惠、焦赞、刘立华见面，起打。"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "焦赞",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺乃焦赞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "任堂惠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杀呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（任堂惠、焦赞同下。）"
        }
      ],
